HEADWORD: Hypocist
<hw>Hyp"o*cist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ a plant
growing on the roots of the <ets>Cistus</ets>.]</ety> <def>An astringent
